Title: An Act Changing the Name of Bugis Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Monroe Joyce Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 751
An Act Changing the Name of Bugis Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Monroe Joyce Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Bugis Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Monroe Joyce Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
